Calling method `pack()` of class `JFrame` will automatically set the preferred sizes for the components inside the `JFrame`. It appears in the code below.

Please also look at [Java coding conventions][1] which allows others to more easily read and understand your code. And note that, according to these conventions, I renamed your class from `button` to `Buttons` and also because there are already several class in the JDK named `Button`.

